WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:01.250
Good morning, family.

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:01.250
I am outside.

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:04.467
We had high winds here in Oklahoma today.

00:00:04.467 --> 00:00:06.600
I'm talking about strong, very unusual winds.

00:00:07.480 --> 00:00:15.400
This little guy, this little squirrel, was up in a tree and he got blown out.

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:30.604
I don't know where his mama went, but he's lying out here on the ground.

00:00:30.604 --> 00:00:39.720
Unfortunately, his sister died in the fall.

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:53.640
I just love nature and I couldn't stand to see him there just die.

00:00:53.640 --> 00:01:06.473
I've never touched a squirrel before that was alive; only the ones that we ate.

00:01:06.473 --> 00:01:26.784
Grandpa would always eat squirrel and cook it up in the frying pan as a boy and make squirrel stew.

00:01:35.120 --> 00:01:36.470
But this is a little squirrel, and I love God's creatures.

00:01:36.470 --> 00:01:51.680
We found him some milk and stuff to try to keep him alive.

00:01:57.400 --> 00:02:41.120
I told my daughter, 'If we can keep him alive and feed him like the lady on the YouTube channel who feeds all the nuts to the squirrels, I'll film him all the time for you all and put it on here.

00:02:41.120 --> 00:03:09.040
' I know our content might get boring; I try not to say the same thing over and over, but that's what's inside of me.

00:03:09.040 --> 00:03:32.000
I told my son, 'I don't want to make boring content; I want it to be inspiring and to lift you up.

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:43.173
' I just know that God is no respecter of persons, and what He did for us, He'll do for you.

00:03:43.173 --> 00:04:08.302
We're a work in progress just like everybody else, but I know that people try to put us on a pedestal.

00:04:08.302 --> 00:04:28.800
I'm just telling you, we're just like you; we're believing for everyday miracles and for the supernatural in our lives.

00:04:40.664 --> 00:04:54.920
I wake up every day with an anticipation that God's going to show up and do something mighty in our lives.

00:04:54.920 --> 00:05:38.880
I told you all I was driving around and the Lord told me great favor was coming on His bride, on His church—that we would see the greatest favor, the greatest impartation of favor on us.

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:46.200
As we walk into the grocery stores, we would walk in favor like you wouldn't believe.

00:05:46.200 --> 00:06:30.560
I believe it's time now for exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think as we enter into the rest this year that God said He was going to do something mighty inside of us.

00:06:30.560 --> 00:07:18.055
I was praying over Israel and what He said about when we walk into churches, that there would be great deliverances for people that are walking in bondage from all kinds of addictions, torments, depression, and anxiety.

00:07:18.055 --> 00:07:42.760
He doesn't want anything missing out of your life; He wants you to be made whole.

00:07:42.760 --> 00:07:59.984
It's not for us to live a busted and disgusted life, but to live a supernatural life.

00:07:59.984 --> 00:08:08.080
Just like Peter, there's stages of glory.

00:08:16.367 --> 00:08:21.080
The Lord showed me it's like first starting out with a single-shot.

00:08:21.080 --> 00:08:22.080
22.

00:08:21.080 --> 00:08:29.680
Then you go to your semi-automatic.

00:08:29.680 --> 00:08:45.907
Both are very lethal, but one has more capacity to do more.

00:08:45.907 --> 00:09:00.828
Then you go to your fully automatic, then to the war guns and artillery.

00:09:00.828 --> 00:09:06.840
There's levels of warfare.

00:09:07.647 --> 00:09:38.800
The Lord showed me that He starts everybody out with a single shot, and if you're faithful with little, He'll make you ruler over the semi-automatic.

00:09:38.800 --> 00:10:04.688
Then He moves you up later in life whenever you're able to handle that amount of glory and power flowing through your life.

00:10:07.400 --> 00:10:28.169
You start operating like Kathryn Kuhlman or Oral Roberts; that level where they operate in a fully automatic machine gun.

00:10:28.169 --> 00:10:49.650
It's an easy way to picture it, but all of it's effective.

00:10:55.229 --> 00:10:58.160
You go from glory to glory.

00:11:13.072 --> 00:11:27.120
I was thinking about how the glory was radiating so much out of Peter that when he walked by, his shadow healed people.

00:11:30.384 --> 00:11:49.440
The glory was so strong on his life that it was coming out of him as far as the circumference of the shadow.

00:11:49.440 --> 00:12:10.380
I said, 'God, what does it take to walk in that kind of anointing?

00:12:10.380 --> 00:12:26.360
' I believe that's what it's going to take in these last days.

00:12:26.360 --> 00:12:26.817
Even greater works will we do than what they did.

00:12:26.817 --> 00:12:50.240
I believe the former and the latter rain are going to come on us in a greater measure than we've ever seen before.

00:12:50.240 --> 00:12:59.520
Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:12:59.520 --> 00:13:18.160
He's still healing the sick, still raising the dead, and still casting out devils.

00:13:18.160 --> 00:13:22.600
But do we believe it?

00:13:22.600 --> 00:13:29.240
Are we doing the Great Commission?

00:13:29.240 --> 00:14:01.855
It's time for us to operate in the Great Commission—going into all the world, laying hands on the sick, casting out devils, and seeing blind eyes open.

00:14:12.876 --> 00:14:13.382
I believe it's time for the supernatural.

00:14:21.507 --> 00:14:35.138
I'm tired of believing for tomorrow; I don't want to go to church and just get a normal message.

00:14:37.495 --> 00:14:42.460
I want to have a radical visitation from the Lord.

00:14:42.460 --> 00:15:04.622
I'm expecting Jesus Christ Himself to come and the glory cloud to show up, or something tangible.

00:15:04.622 --> 00:15:47.080
I'm hungry for the manifestations of God, not so that I can just fill myself up like what I get when I go to Billy Burke, but expecting that glory to cross-pollinate on me.

00:15:47.080 --> 00:16:02.542
Whenever I lay hands on the sick, I see full manifestation too.

00:16:10.809 --> 00:16:18.264
I want a tangible presence of the fire of the Lord to set the captives free.

00:16:18.264 --> 00:16:38.440
I don't want to say this is a 'unicorn' experience; I want all of us to walk this way.

00:16:38.440 --> 00:16:53.280
If there is any sick among you, let him call for the elders of the church.

00:17:06.240 --> 00:17:19.307
The body of Christ shouldn't be walking in any kind of sickness or demonic oppression from drugs, alcohol, or addictions of any kind.

00:17:32.140 --> 00:17:48.600
The Bible said He's coming for a church without spot or wrinkle, and I believe in the Tommy Hicks vision that the glorious church is rising up.

00:17:48.600 --> 00:18:17.000
When Billy Burke talks about people falling under the power, there should be a manifested change in our lives.

00:18:17.000 --> 00:18:29.369
I don't want to do church as usual; I want to do church unusual.

00:18:33.040 --> 00:18:38.920
I want to be radical for Jesus.

00:18:38.920 --> 00:18:46.680
I get so tired of lukewarm church.

00:18:46.680 --> 00:18:52.840
Aren't you hungry for more?

00:18:52.840 --> 00:19:14.200
Instead of always believing for your miracle, you should bring it and take it to the rest of the world.

00:19:14.200 --> 00:19:29.265
I'm a believing believer that signs follow them that believe.

00:19:34.576 --> 00:19:46.412
The Earth is groaning for the manifested sons and daughters to be the salt and the light.

00:19:51.160 --> 00:19:53.260
I want to pay the price.

00:19:51.160 --> 00:20:02.552
Father, show me how to go from glory to glory.

00:20:02.552 --> 00:20:12.396
We're taking back the land and making war against the devil.

00:20:12.396 --> 00:20:24.607
Satan, you are not going to take any more land from us.

00:20:24.607 --> 00:20:25.040
We're giant slayers.

00:20:25.040 --> 00:20:38.504
Do you believe God has called you for such a time as this?

00:20:38.504 --> 00:20:46.200
If He did it for John G.

00:20:46.200 --> 00:20:58.102
Lake, Smith Wigglesworth, or AA Allen back in the tent revivals, He'll do it today.

00:20:58.102 --> 00:21:08.320
He said, 'I'm uncapping the wells of revival, Brandon.

00:21:23.360 --> 00:21:27.910
A greater revival than what you've ever seen before is about to happen.

00:21:23.360 --> 00:22:03.120
' I'm passionate because when you see so many broken people, you know the only thing that's ever going to help them is a revelation of the knowledge of the Word.

00:22:03.120 --> 00:22:08.040
I want that switch on all the time.

00:22:16.320 --> 00:22:23.280
I know the hotter that fire gets on the inside of you, the more it's going to change you.

00:22:23.280 --> 00:22:30.320
I'm seeking it every day.

00:22:35.520 --> 00:22:41.760
I just want to eat it like a dog on a T-bone.

00:22:41.760 --> 00:22:53.560
I'm not giving up until I'm radically changed from the inside out.

00:22:53.560 --> 00:27:58.120
That's where Diana and I are at, and we refuse to stay where we were two years ago.

00:28:14.100 --> 00:28:46.097
I want to stir you up and let you know there's hope.

00:28:46.097 --> 00:30:18.080
There's light at the end of the tunnel, and your circumstance is going to change today.

00:30:18.080 --> 00:30:30.003
I laid hands on all those pictures all afternoon.

00:30:30.003 --> 00:31:07.280
Even my mother-in-law is here and she was praying for you.

00:31:07.280 --> 00:31:42.329
We're believing believers who are fully persuaded that God's going to do something in your life today.

00:31:42.329 --> 00:31:52.160
Father, we thank you.

00:31:52.160 --> 00:32:28.120
We call those things that be not as though they were.

00:33:08.080 --> 00:33:14.120
We call people healed and whole in the name of Jesus.

00:33:14.120 --> 00:33:35.511
We release financial blessing and favor over their households.

00:33:35.511 --> 00:33:45.195
We release increase and multiplication.

00:33:45.195 --> 00:34:59.040
Father, they have more than enough to give to the kingdom of God and promote the gospel.

00:34:59.040 --> 00:36:01.080
We pray a hedge over President Trump today as he's headed home.

00:36:01.080 --> 00:36:20.784
I thank you for a blessing and supernatural restoration on him to lead this nation into victory.

00:36:37.480 --> 00:36:49.796
As the stock market crashes and people say 'the sky is falling' like Chicken Little, we know the best is yet to come.

00:36:49.796 --> 00:36:53.178
Help us to be in sync with you all the time.

00:36:53.178 --> 00:37:16.720
Father, I thank you for what you showed me: the earthquakes, the tsunami, the crop drought, and a new kind of energy source.

00:37:16.720 --> 00:37:28.280
I saw prophetic significance in the blood moon last night.

00:37:28.280 --> 00:37:43.344
I could feel a tangible presence of the Lord in the atmosphere.

00:37:43.344 --> 00:38:15.936
We must pray over America for a 'Red Dawn.

00:38:15.936 --> 00:38:53.040
' We must pray for these secret cells of people, the moles and the rats within America.

00:38:53.040 --> 00:39:11.360
I believe the baptism of the Holy Spirit is for every single one of you.

00:39:11.360 --> 00:39:22.760
Acts chapter 2 is still going on today.

00:39:22.760 --> 00:39:36.700
If you want to learn more, get the book 'Why Tongues?

00:39:36.700 --> 00:39:44.440
' by Kenneth E.

00:39:44.440 --> 00:39:46.189
Hagin.

00:40:06.240 --> 00:40:15.992
I'm going to pray in the spirit now, and I'm going to yield to the Holy Spirit.

00:40:15.992 --> 00:40:23.497
Lord, show us that which is to come.

00:40:23.497 --> 00:40:27.440
As the watchman on the wall, He shows us things ahead of time.

00:40:27.440 --> 00:40:33.080
Father, we yield to you.

00:40:33.080 --> 00:40:57.360
Give us eyes to see in the realm of the spirit and ears to hear what the Spirit is saying.

00:40:57.360 --> 00:41:32.840
I see drought; I'm in Amarillo and all around Lubbock, we call the rain in Jesus' name.

00:41:32.840 --> 00:42:02.920
I thank you for the rain, the former and the latter rain.

00:42:02.920 --> 00:42:50.680
I see another wave of glory, a fresh fire in the name of Jesus on the land.

00:42:50.680 --> 00:42:57.280
All hidden things be revealed.

00:43:02.320 --> 00:43:07.880
I see it in the pulpits and in the churches.

00:43:22.920 --> 00:43:26.070
You will not put new wine in old wineskins.

00:43:22.920 --> 00:43:47.520
I see the oil of the Holy Spirit softening the old wineskins, making them soft and pliable again.

00:43:47.520 --> 00:44:03.640
It's time to rise up and be the voice.

00:44:03.640 --> 00:44:38.720
Don't parrot what you heard in the past; it's time to speak new words at last.

00:44:38.720 --> 00:44:48.825
Jump in the river and flow.

00:44:48.825 --> 00:45:06.407
Get on a Holy Ghost inner tube and go down that river.

00:45:06.407 --> 00:45:11.440
Drink big.

00:45:11.440 --> 00:45:23.235
There's rain coming to the Panhandle.

00:45:23.235 --> 00:45:49.080
I hear the sound of an abundance of rain throughout the land.

00:45:49.080 --> 00:46:13.760
From coast to coast, there will be a mighty rushing wind and cloven tongues of fire.

00:46:13.760 --> 00:46:26.507
It's time to get in your Holy Ghost inner tube.

00:46:26.507 --> 00:46:36.905
Out of your belly shall flow rivers of living water.

00:46:36.905 --> 00:46:44.127
Stir yourself up by praying in the spirit.

00:46:44.127 --> 00:47:03.960
Shake off that victim mentality; you are a victor.

00:47:03.960 --> 00:47:14.671
Get the old 'stinking thinking' and religious thinking out.

00:47:14.671 --> 00:47:21.347
Come out of that box.

00:47:21.347 --> 00:47:35.845
New wine is bubbling up out of your spirit.

00:47:35.845 --> 00:47:44.960
It's a time of refreshing for the church.

00:47:44.960 --> 00:48:07.560
We speak to the Canadian government and their Prime Minister; they need a touch.

00:48:07.560 --> 00:48:21.664
Lord, we thank you that you're touching Elon Musk and touching Trump.

00:48:21.664 --> 00:48:31.460
We speak to the financial outpouring.

00:48:31.460 --> 00:48:51.520
Satan, get your hands off of our money now in Jesus' name.

00:48:51.520 --> 00:49:03.240
Release the children of God's money for the great wealth transfer.

00:49:03.240 --> 00:49:08.480
There is no dam holding back the money.

00:49:08.480 --> 00:49:25.680
I heard them plotting in Russia; they don't want to be underneath the West's influence anymore.

00:49:25.680 --> 00:49:34.812
I see the BRICS nations wanting to rise up.

00:49:35.240 --> 00:49:50.133
The Beast system is rising up in the days ahead.

00:49:50.133 --> 00:50:15.160
Watch Easter; I'm believing that a new well of revival is going to start to spring up.

00:50:15.160 --> 00:50:32.240
Just like Paul and Silas praying in the midnight hour, there was a great shaking in that jail cell.

00:50:32.240 --> 00:50:45.600
The jail cell of your circumstances is coming open today.

00:50:45.600 --> 00:50:55.434
Those chains are falling off as you worship and praise.

00:51:07.600 --> 00:51:10.050
The days of fun have just begun.

00:51:07.600 --> 00:51:16.269
We'll be back tomorrow and we'll pray again.

00:51:16.269 --> 00:51:31.960
I've got to pray more in the spirit because that's what gets the job done.

00:51:31.960 --> 00:51:47.320
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:51:47.320 --> 00:51:53.880
Jesus loves you so much.

00:51:53.880 --> 00:52:04.040
God bless you all and we'll see you again tomorrow.

00:52:04.040 --> 00:52:05.040
Bye-bye.
